description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a professional, ambitious &amp; confident Mental Health Nurse / RMN to join our dedicated bank team as a based at our specialist personality disorders service in Gloucester.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be working as a Bank Nurse at Cygnet Alders Clinic.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Cygnet Alders Clinic is a 20 bed rehabilitation service providing assessment, treatment and rehabilitation for women with personality disorder and complex needs. Cygnet Alders Clinic is on the Welsh Hospital Framework with specialist service status.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you’re passionate about what you do, we want to talk to you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Day-to-Day…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Produce outstanding written reports based on your nursing assessments and observations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with the management team to develop the service, audit, and improve quality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Under NMC guidelines, ensure that individual care plans are complete &amp; maintained collectively with residents, relatives and other healthcare professionals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Administer prescribed medicines with Healthcare procedure and Healthcare Commission guidelines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You are…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Open, compassionate, honest &amp; resilient mental health nurse / RMN that is able capable of maintaining documentation and undertaking audits.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Well informed of the Mental Health Act 1983 &amp; have an understanding of latest nursing practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Focused on patient recovery to monitor, manage &amp; reduce risk. Able to help empower &amp; support service user independence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Cygnet? We’ll offer you…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NHS &amp; employee discount scheme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;50% NMC registration renewal paid by Cygnet&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free meals on duty&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free parking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;RCNi membership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bespoke career pathways&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plus much more&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Cygnet Health Care has been providing a national network of high quality specialist mental health services for more than 30 years.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Cygnet Alders Clinicprovides a specialist psychologically informed personality disorder pathway across three living areas; Severn, for assessment and stabilisation; Avon, where residents move as they engage and progress with their treatment pathway; and Coln, which focuses on transitioning to the community.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Alders is rated‘&lt;strong&gt;Good’&lt;/strong&gt; by the &lt;strong&gt;CQC&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you a Mental Health Nurse / RMN that is ready to make a positive change?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Click on the ‘apply now’ link below.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join us!&lt;/p&gt;
